# AssetGuard Pro — Visão Geral do Sistema

## Arquitetura Geral

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Frontend["Frontend (Vite + React)"]
        Login["Login"]
        Dashboard["Dashboard"]
        Inventory["Almoxarifado"]
        Assets["Ativos"]
        Scanner["Scanner"]
        Users["Usuários"]
        Departments["Setores"]
        Audit["Auditoria"]
    end

    subgraph Services["Camada de Serviço"]
        DS["DataService"]
        Auth["AuthContext"]
    end

    subgraph Backend["Backend (Next.js 14 — porta 3001)"]
        AuthAPI["/api/auth"]
        ProductsAPI["/api/products"]
        AssetsAPI["/api/assets"]
        DashboardAPI["/api/dashboard"]
        UsersAPI["/api/users"]
        DeptAPI["/api/departments"]
        LogsAPI["/api/logs"]
    end

    subgraph Database["PostgreSQL"]
        DB[("assetguard")]
    end

    Login --> Auth
    Auth -->|JWT| DS
    Dashboard --> DS
    Inventory --> DS
    Assets --> DS
    Scanner --> DS
    Users --> DS
    Departments --> DS
    Audit --> DS

    DS -->|HTTP + Bearer Token| AuthAPI
    DS -->|HTTP + Bearer Token| ProductsAPI
    DS -->|HTTP + Bearer Token| AssetsAPI
    DS -->|HTTP + Bearer Token| DashboardAPI
    DS -->|HTTP + Bearer Token| UsersAPI
    DS -->|HTTP + Bearer Token| DeptAPI
    DS -->|HTTP + Bearer Token| LogsAPI

    AuthAPI --> DB
    ProductsAPI --> DB
    AssetsAPI --> DB
    DashboardAPI --> DB
    UsersAPI --> DB
    DeptAPI --> DB
    LogsAPI --> DB

    style Frontend fill:#dbeafe,stroke:#3b82f6
    style Backend fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#22c55e
    style Database fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#f59e0b
    style Services fill:#f3e8ff,stroke:#a855f7
```

---

## Modelo de Dados (ER Diagram)

```mermaid
erDiagram
    User {
        String id PK
        String username UK
        String password
        String fullName
        Role role "ADMIN | OPERATOR"
        Boolean isActive
        DateTime createdAt
    }

    Product {
        String id PK
        String name
        String barcode UK
        Int quantity
        Int minStock
        String location
        String category
        Float unitValue
        DateTime createdAt
        DateTime updatedAt
    }

    StockMovement {
        String id PK
        String productId FK
        MovementType type "ENTRADA | SAIDA"
        Int quantity
        Float unitCost "nullable"
        String reason
        String departmentId FK "nullable"
        String userId
        String userName
        DateTime createdAt
    }

    Asset {
        String id PK
        String assetTag UK
        String serialNumber UK
        String name
        String description
        DateTime acquisitionDate
        Float purchaseValue
        String location
        AssetStatus status "IN_USE | MAINTENANCE | DISPOSED | AVAILABLE"
        Int usefulLifeYears
        DateTime createdAt
        DateTime updatedAt
    }

    AuditLog {
        String id PK
        DateTime timestamp
        String userId FK
        String userName
        LogAction action "LOGIN | CREATE | UPDATE | DELETE | MOVEMENT_IN | MOVEMENT_OUT"
        TargetType targetType "PRODUCT | ASSET | SYSTEM | USER | DEPARTMENT"
        String targetId "nullable"
        String details
    }

    Department {
        String id PK
        String name
        String costCenterCode UK
        Boolean isActive
        DateTime createdAt
        DateTime updatedAt
    }

    User ||--o{ AuditLog : "registra"
    Product ||--o{ StockMovement : "possui"
    Department ||--o{ StockMovement : "recebe"
```

